# File Naming Conventions

- **Event classes:** PascalCase with `Event` suffix (e.g. `VillagerEvent`, `ShopkeeperEvent`)
- **Hook files:** camelCase (e.g. `player.ts`, `server.ts`, `client.ts`)
- **Database items:** PascalCase (e.g. `Potion.ts`, `IronSword.ts`)
- **Spritesheets:** PascalCase (e.g. `Characters.ts`, `Monsters.ts`)
- **GUI components:** PascalCase (e.g. `DialogUi.vue`, `MenuUi.vue`)
